posting_body: ['The Woods of Burnsville', '14701 Portland Ave, Burnsville, MN, 55306', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 4', 'OR Text', '4', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text us.', 'Want more information?', 'Follow this link:', '<URL>', 'Welcome to The Woods of Burnsville', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 773 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'The Woods of Burnsville Apartments offer the best value in apartment living in the Burnsville, Minnesota area.', 'We are committed to your comfort and convenience.', 'Enjoy prompt service from our professional staff, and benefit from our extraordinary community features including a resident clubhouse with a 24-hour fitness center, sparkling swimming pool, sports courts, and more!', 'Choose from newly renovated spacious studio, 1, 2 or 3 bedroom apartment homes with amenities including private decks and patios, walk-in closets, and modern interior finishes.', 'Our apartment homes are located in a park-like setting, yet just minutes from the Twin Cities.', 'With convenient access to I-35 you can get where you need to be easily.', 'Enjoy great shopping, dining, and entertainment all within a short ride.', "With a full range of luxury amenities and premier location, you'll feel right at home.", 'Office Hours:', 'Monday: 9:00am-6:00pm', 'Tuesday:', '9:00am-6:00pm', 'Wednesday: 9:00am-6:00pm', 'Thursday: 9:00am-6:00pm', 'Friday:', '9:00am-6:00pm', 'Saturday: 10:00am-5:00pm', 'Sunday: Closed', 'Uffrrn2xSIR']
